      "releaseNotes": "Bug Fixes and Improvements! We've tackled several bugs and polished the app for a smoother, more reliable experience.\n\nHappy tracking and stay healthy!\n\nThank you for updating the app.\n\nAlways yours,\nThe MyNetDiary Team",
